---
const steps = [
  ["Intent", "说出真正想改变的事情"],
  ["Task", "转化为可负责的工作"],
  ["Action", "由人和 Agent 共同执行"],
  ["Evidence", "用事实与产物证明结果"],
  ["Decision", "人在关键节点做判断"],
  ["Knowledge", "把经验写回组织"]
];
---

<section class="work-loop section" id="loop">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-copy compact-copy" data-reveal>
      <h2>工作，不再消失在对话里。</h2>
      <p>每一个模糊意图，都能成为有目标、有责任、有过程、有证据，并且能继续生长的工作。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="loop-stage" data-reveal>
      <svg class="loop-wire" viewBox="0 0 1200 230" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M45 115H1155"></path>
        <path class="active" d="M45 115H1155"></path>
      </svg>
      <div class="loop-items">
        {steps.map(([name, detail]) => (
          <article class="loop-item">
            <span class="loop-point"></span>
            <strong>{name}</strong>
            <p>{detail}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="loop-return"><span>下一项工作</span><i></i></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
